title: 'N/A'
body: The overall product feels very well made, appropriate for its price as a step up to the typical boxes you'd find on Amazon between $15-30. However, there are still some quality issues that come with not spending more that you might want to consider before purchasing. For one, the hinge is pretty garbage. I have my worries about it lasting particularly long and staying up consistently. Second, each watch slot is not equally sized nor are the pillows. Lastly, as other reviews have mentioned, is that these boxes can still be somewhat easily damaged. Fortunately, that last point doesn't relate to me, but just something to think about.
